# Skill: Code Review

Perform a **two-pass** review of the current branch vs default branch.

Use `.ai/lifecycle/review.md` as the review contract and `.ai/lifecycle/test.md` to verify validation gaps.

## Pass 1 — Blocking

- Security (XSS, unsafe HTML, token storage)
- Auth/session edge cases
- Data correctness and error handling
- Accessibility regressions (labels, roles, focus)
- Performance foot-guns (unnecessary re-renders, huge bundles)

## Pass 2 — Nits

- Naming, file placement, duplication
- Test coverage gaps for new logic
- Inconsistent use of generated `.ai/rules/` guidance
- Missing lifecycle or adapter updates when templates changed

Use `.ai/skills/code-review/checklist.md` as the authoritative list.

## Output

- Findings first, ordered by severity.
- File and line references when possible.
- Missing tests or manual checks.
- Ready/not-ready judgment.
